6919::$$$message_0063_0000_0000$$$::"SHINJI!!!"[lr]::
6920::$$$message_0063_0000_0001$$$::I close in on him.[lr]::
6921::$$$message_0063_0000_0002$$$::He has no shadows protecting him.[lr]::
6922::$$$message_0063_0000_0003$$$::Just a few more steps...maybe three more meters, and I can[line2]::
6923::$$$message_0063_0001_0000$$$::"S-stop! Don't come near me!"[lr]::
6924::$$$message_0063_0001_0001$$$::Shinji turns and runs.[lr]::
6925::$$$message_0063_0001_0002$$$::The moment I reach out to grab his back...[lr]::
6926::$$$message_0063_0001_0003$$$::"Gh[line2]!?"[lr]::
6927::$$$message_0063_0001_0004$$$::I feel a chill run through my entire body, and I quickly jerk my arm back.::
6928::$$$message_0063_0002_0000$$$::Something cuts through the air.[lr]::
6929::$$$message_0063_0002_0001$$$::A black blade slices through the space I'd been occupying just an instant before.::
6930::$$$message_0063_0003_0000$$$::"Guh...!"[lr]::
6931::$$$message_0063_0003_0001$$$::I stop.[lr]::
6932::$$$message_0063_0003_0002$$$::I don't know where she came from, but standing in front of me now...::
6933::$$$message_0063_0004_0000$$$::...I see the woman dressed in ominous black so dark even the most venomous shade of crimson seems pale in comparison.::
6934::$$$message_0063_0005_0000$$$::"Ah..."[lr]::
6935::$$$message_0063_0005_0001$$$::My mind goes blank with fear.[lr]::
6936::$$$message_0063_0005_0002$$$::I'm going to die.[lr]::
6937::$$$message_0063_0005_0003$$$::I don't want to think about it, but the image of my own brutal death fills my head.[lr]::
6938::$$$message_0063_0005_0004$$$::   I sense it.[lr]::
6939::$$$message_0063_0005_0005$$$::I sense only death... The shadows earlier were nothing like this.::
